desc: Online clothing store for people with skin conditions like eczema, psoriasis, postherpetic neuralgia, and more. Focused on materials that are soft, safe, and flattering.

layout.text: Online boutique for people with sensitive skin like eczema, psoriasis, or other dermatitis issues. We sell clothes like bamboo shirts, cotton dresses, and linen trousers. Empowered Eczema digital products are also sold here.
